{comment: Verse 1}
[C]Here's to the ones [G]that we got
[Am]Cheers to the wish [Em]you were here, but you're not
'Cause the [F]drinks bring back [C]all the memories
Of [F]everything we've [G]been through
[C]Toast to the ones [G]here today
[Am]Toast to the ones [Em]that we lost on the way
'Cause the [F]drinks bring back [C]all the memories
